INSTALLATION

If not already unpacked, unpack Pairtree with

   tar xzf Pairtree-0.2.tar.gz

after adjusting the version number as needed.

To install the module and script, type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

For the "make install" you may have to become the superuser, as in,

   sudo make install


